#12500
Falling into a Void~
As you climb down into the hole in the ground, a sense of vertigo washes
over you and you feel as if time and space are melting around you. Suddenly,
there is nothing but blackness around you, although below there seems to
be a faint light in the distance.
~
0 8205 0
D5
The blackness continues in this direction as well, although a small hint of
light appears to be shining in this direction.
~
~
