#12501
Passing into the Light~
After continuing on for what seems like ages towards the light you finally
reach it only to be once again blasted by vertigo and into the light with
a swirling vortex in front of you, leaving no choice but to proced.
~
0 8205 0
D0
In this direction the blackness seems to end in a swirling vortex of light,
you have no choice but to procede in this direction.
~
~
