#12537
Serena's Bedroom~
Princess Serena's Bedroom looks about what you'd expect of a girl half her
age, definetly not what you'd expect of a Princess from one of the most
powerful kingdoms in the Solar System. The room is painted in a gaudy bright
pink that makes your eyes hurt, and in the center of the room is a large
canopied bed which is also, *ugh*, pink and has many stuffed animals on it
including a HUGE white bunny rabbit. This truly does look like a child's room
and not one of a maturing Princess.
