The Second Floor of the Guardhouse~
This room is surprisingly cleaner than you would have expected judging
from what you saw downstairs, no clothes are tossed around, nothing is
out of place, all that is here are the bunks lined up against three of
the walls and the chests containing the guards belongings lined up against
the fourth wall, simply amazing!
